column4: Thanks to the efforts of all, the Lunar Hopopolis has been completed. Feel free to explore while we prepare for future endeavors!
column5: I present to you our interstellar port town: Lunar Hopopolis, home of the cosmic explorers! We thank you all for your cooperation!

column4: Owing to myriad contributions by artisans like you, we have achieved every last objective outlined for Sinus Ardorum. Enjoy a well earned rest, and stay alert for future updates!
column5: Owing to myriad contributions by artisans like you, we have achieved every last objective outlined for Sinus Ardorum. You've made my dream come true!
